      • getScheduler

        public Scheduler getScheduler()
        Description copied from class: Interpreter
        Interpreter can implements it's own scheduler by overriding this method. There're two default scheduler provided, FIFO, Parallel. If your interpret() can handle concurrent request, use Parallel or use FIFO. You can get default scheduler by using SchedulerFactory.singleton().createOrGetFIFOScheduler() SchedulerFactory.singleton().createOrGetParallelScheduler()
        Overrides:
        getScheduler in class Interpreter
        Returns:
        return scheduler instance. This method can be called multiple times and have to return the same instance. Can not return null.
